	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">微软要把单手键盘带给 iPhone，扇形的</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-17 07:00:41 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
